'''桑迪·莫里斯'''（Sandi Morris，{{bd|1992年|7月8日||}}）是一名美国女子[[撑杆跳高|撑杆跳高]]运动员<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iaaf.org/athletes/united-states/sandi-morris-250533 |title=Sandi Morris |publisher=IAAF |date=23 August 2015 |accessdate=23 August 2015 |archive-date=2016-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917160351/https://www.iaaf.org/athletes/united-states/sandi-morris-250533 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的最佳成绩是5.00米，是2016年9月9日在[[布魯塞爾|布魯塞爾]]创造的<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/AthleticsSweden/status/728621740742545409 |title=2016 Doha Diamond League video of world leading jump in pole vault |accessdate=2016-08-25 |archive-date=2018-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002161814/https://twitter.com/AthleticsSweden/status/728621740742545409 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iaaf.org/athletes/united-states/sandi-morris-250533|title=Sandi Morris|work=iaaf.org|accessdate=March 18, 2016|archive-date=2016-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917160351/https://www.iaaf.org/athletes/united-states/sandi-morris-250533|dead-url=no}}</ref>。以4.85米的成绩赢得2016年[[里约奥运会|里约奥运会]]女子撑杆跳高[[银牌|银牌]]。

